Dennis Kigiri, Department of Animal Sciences, Egerton University.
****Chicken rearing
I want to start indigenous chicken rearing, what advise can you give me? 
Shadrack, Nyamira
Chicken production is critical for improving food and nutritional security at the home level by providing high-quality meat and eggs.
You don’t require a lot of money to start keeping indigenous chickens, since they can be fed on available feeds at home, they are hardy and resistant to some diseases, and have tasty products.



