If housed well and their feeds supplemented, they perform better. You can raise cocks for sale especially during the festive season and hens for eggs and multiplication.
There are improved Kienyeji chickens that perform better than local chickens in terms of egg production and growth rate.
Dennis Kigiri, Department of Animal Sciences, Egerton University.
